FBIS4-19385 "drweu074_q_94012" FBIS-WEU-94-074 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 TURKEY Violence in Israel, Occupied Territories Condemned Violence in Israel, Occupied Territories Condemned TA1604065894 Ankara Turkiye Radyolari Network in Turkish 2000 GMT 15 Apr 94 TA1604065894 Ankara Turkiye Radyolari Network Turkish BFN [Text] Turkey has announced that the escalating violence in Israel and in the occupied territories cause concern. In a statement, the Foreign Ministry strongly condemned the mutual attacks being perpetrated by extremists and causing the death of innocent Israelis and Palestinians. The statement says: It must be understood by all that terrorism will not help achieve any legitimate aims. We call on the sides to jointly fight terrorism and to cooperate in order not to halt the negotiating process at this critical stage of the peace negotiations. We hope that the terrorist activities which intensified in recent days are not repeated.
